General.Name: Nordstrom Inc
General.Description: Nordstrom, Inc. operates as a fashion retailer in the United States. The company provides apparel, shoes, beauty, accessories, and home goods for women, men, young adults, and children. It also offers a range of third-party and private-label merchandise through various channels, such as Nordstrom stores, and Nordstrom.com website and mobile application; Nordstrom Rack stores; Nordstrom Locals; NordstromRack.com website and mobile application; and clearance stores under the Last Chance name. Nordstrom, Inc. was founded in 1901 and is headquartered in Seattle, Washington. As of May 20, 2025, Nordstrom, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of El Puerto de Liverpool, S.A.B. de C.V.
